      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_012_000069",
    "sentence": "詔以襄成王子白澤襲爵樂陵王。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_012_000070",
    "sentence": "齊亡，入關，徙蜀死。",
    "entities": [
